    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>We're proud to unveil the much-anticipated collaboration between two icons of the golf world: J.Lindeberg and Glenmuir. This capsule collection, available at TRENDYGOLF, unites Glenmuir's enduring heritage with J.Lindeberg's sleek, contemporary aesthetic, delivering a collection of golf apparel that is both rooted in tradition and at the forefront of modern innovation.</em></p><p>In this comprehensive guide, we'll dive into the inspirations behind the collection, examine the unique design features of the men's and women's pieces, and explore how the collaboration captures the spirit of Scotland's storied landscapes. Plus, we'll introduce Todd Clements, the rising star of professional golf and face of the campaign, whose commitment to excellence perfectly embodies the spirit of the J.Lindeberg x Glenmuir collaboration.</p><p></p><h2><strong>A Fusion of Craftsmanship and Innovation</strong></h2><p>The J.Lindeberg x Glenmuir collaboration encapsulates a meeting of two distinct yet harmonious design philosophies. Glenmuir, with a heritage spanning more than 130 years, is known for its rich legacy in the world of golf apparel. Founded in 1891 in the heart of Scotland, Glenmuir's dedication to quality craftsmanship and timeless design has made it a favourite among golfers who value classic elegance on the green.</p><p>J.Lindeberg, on the other hand, has revolutionised the sportswear industry with its fusion of Scandinavian minimalism and high-performance functionality. Since its inception in 1996, J.Lindeberg has been committed to pushing the boundaries of style and technology, creating apparel that is as functional as it is fashionable. This collaboration between J.Lindeberg and Glenmuir blends these two brands' unique strengths, offering golfers a collection that honours the past while embracing the future.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
