          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4><strong>Performance Polo with Advanced Fabric Technology</strong></h4><p>The women's collection is designed with the modern golfer in mind, balancing style and functionality with ease. The <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-glenmuir-womens-alina-polo-moonbeam-ps25?_fid=f05d5c905&_pos=3&_ss=c&variant=50397087891740\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Women's Alina Polo</span></a>, a standout piece, is crafted from advanced fabric technology that ensures superior comfort and breathability. With a streamlined silhouette and a range of colours to choose from, this polo is designed to support peak performance on the course without compromising on style. It's a piece that every golfer will appreciate.</p><h4><strong>Merino Polo for Timeless Elegance</strong></h4><p>For those looking for something with a touch of timeless elegance, the <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/collections/j-lindeberg-x-glenmuir-women-s-golf-collection?_pos=3&_psq=glenmuir&_ss=e&_v=1.0&filter.v.availability=1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Amandine Polo</span></a> is a must-have. Made from premium fabrics, this polo offers not only the warmth and softness of merino wool but also a refined look that is versatile enough for any golfing occasion. This piece truly captures the essence of the collaboration, combining traditional materials with contemporary design for a look that feels both classic and modern.</p><h4><strong>Playsuits & Dresses for Style and Mobility</strong></h4><p>Designed with the active golfer in mind, the <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/products/x-glenmuir-womens-kendra-playsuit-navy-ps25?_fid=f05d5c905&_pos=7&_ss=c&variant=50397045981468\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Women's Kendra Playsuit</span></a> is as functional as it is stylish. Made with a blend of high-performance materials, this playsuit offers unparalleled ease of movement, ensuring that nothing hinders your swing. Available in neutral tones, it's a versatile piece that pairs effortlessly with other items in the collection, making it essential for any female golfer looking to combine style and functionality on the green.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
