            "text": "<p>From its luxurious textures to its innovative designs, the J.Lindeberg x Glenmuir collection is a celebration of Scottish knitwear and Scandinavian design. Each piece in the collection is carefully crafted, reflecting the collaboration's dedication to quality, style, and performance. This unique fusion of past and present, tradition and innovation, offers golfers of all levels a wardrobe that is as practical as it is stylish.</p>"
