    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Todd Clements: The Perfect Ambassador for the J.Lindeberg x Glenmuir Collaboration",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every collaboration needs a face that embodies its values, and for the J.Lindeberg x Glenmuir capsule, that face is professional golfer Todd Clements. Turning professional in 2018, Todd has quickly risen through the ranks of professional golf, demonstrating a dedication to his craft that mirrors J.Lindeberg's own commitment to excellence.</p><p>From winning the English Amateur Championship in 2017 to achieving his first European Tour victory at the D+D Real Czech Masters in August 2023, Todd's journey is a testament to the power of perseverance, self-improvement, and a willingness to push the boundaries of the sport. As a J.Lindeberg ambassador since 2022, Todd embodies the spirit of this collection, representing both the timeless elegance of Glenmuir and the modern edge of J.Lindeberg.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
